Hannah Taylor-Gordon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_Taylor-Gordon 0 Hannah Taylor-Gordon (born 6 March 1987) is an English actress. She made her film debut in the 1993 film The House of the Spirits. She is best known for her role as Anne Frank in the TV miniseries Anne Frank: The Whole Story for which she received both an Emmy and a Golden Globe nomination. She recently played Lady Macbeth in the low-budget award-winning film version of The Tragedy of Macbeth. Hannah_Taylor-Gordon ( born_6_March_1987 ) is an_English_actress .
